com.tailf.jnc
Class SchemaNode

java.lang.Object
  com.tailf.jnc.SchemaNode

public class SchemaNode
extends java.lang.Object

The SchemaNode class is used to represent individual nodes in the schema tree. Each generated ConfM namespace gets its schema, as a set of SchemaNode objects generated in its top class All the SchemaNode's for a namespace are put into hashtable that is held by the SchemaTree class.
